    <img src="pics/Dot.gif" width="20" height="20"> Screen Services offers a variety of stainless steel and synthetic material screening solutions, including wedgewire, wire mesh, perforated plate, polyurethane screens, and cyclone media separators. Screen Services works with consulting and engineering firms, as well as end users, offering assistance, insight, and specific solutions for screening, filtering, and sieving problems. <br> <br>

     Screen Services' high quality wedge wire products are found in all industries where reliable phase (solid/liquid/gas) separation is required. We also supply fine wire mesh and perforated plate in small pieces to full rolls/sheets, and in fabricated form, circles, or special shapes, in a wide variety of metal alloys and synthetic materials.<img src="pics/Dot.gif" width="20" height="20"> <br> 
